about him. He was perplexed and di&s;tre&s;&s;|ed.
"This &s;um then," &s;aid he to him&s;elf,
"would make this poor family completely
happy&mdash;it is in my power to give it&mdash;to
make them completely happy! But what
is to become of me?&mdash;how &s;hall I contrive
to reach home with the little money that
